    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;Speex is an open-source voice codec suitable for use in VoIP (Voice over IP) type applications.  This document describes the payload format for Speex-generated bit streams within an RTP packet.  Also included here are the necessary details for the use of Speex with the Session Description Protocol (SDP). [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
